You can create a group of friends or family members who are also using the app, and then invite them to join you in an exercise session. During the session, you will be able to see each other's progress on the screen and compete against one another if you want. This feature helps to make exercising more fun and engaging, as well as provide motivation and support from others.

Here are some examples of how you could use ശേഷം ചോദ്യം:

* Invite your friends to join you in a yoga class and follow along with you on the screen.
* Create a running club with your coworkers and track each other's progress during a workout.
* Have a fitness competition with your family members and see who can complete the most exercises in a certain amount of time.

To use ശേഷം ചോദ്യം, simply go to the "Exercises" section of the app and select the exercise you want to do. Then, tap the "Create Group" button and enter the names of the people you want to invite. Once everyone has joined the group, you can start the exercise session by tapping the "Start" button. The app will then display the progress of each member of the group on the screen, so you can see how everyone is doing.
